                     <interp inst="t18210606-1-person84" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , ESQ. I am deputy keeper of the State Papers. I know 
               <persName id="t18210606-1-person85">
                  John 
                  Bruce
               <interp inst="t18210606-1-person85" type="surname" value="Bruce"></interp>
