                     <interp inst="t18210606-1-person85" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Esq. lives in the parish of St. Mary Abbotts, Kensington.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I leave it to my Counsel.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18210606-1-verdict7" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210606-1-verdict7" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
